Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:16.50,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{Huey, once we reach the hospital, \Nyou can get some rest.}Huey, cố chịu đựng đến khi tới bệnh viện đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:17.92,Default,Huey,0,0,0,,{Thank you, ma'am.}Cảm ơn bà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:23.29,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{A traveling carnival, eh?}Lễ hội đường phố à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.42,Default,Bianca,0,0,0,,{You wanted to see that, didn't you? How lucky.}Anh cũng muốn xem mà nhỉ? Tốt nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.80,Default,Donald,0,0,0,,{What's lucky about these legs?}May gì với cái chân này?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.73,Default,Nean1,0,0,0,,{I'm very sorry.}Tôi rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.38,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Huh? For what?}Hả? Chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.72,Default,Nean1,0,0,0,,{We will need to inspect your carry-on luggage.}Chúng tôi sẽ xách hành lý cho quý khách.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.59,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Should we not have brought the chocolate?}Không được mang socola hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.07,Default,Nean1,0,0,0,,{This way.}Lối này ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.66,Default,Nean1,0,0,0,,{Right in here.}Bên đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.41,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Why, thank you.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.68,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're...}Anh là...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:01.24,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Ah, I get it.}A, hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.25,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I see you did your job. Good for you.}Anh đã vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:05.17,Default,Smith,0,0,0,,{Got Viola's id?}ID của Viola đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.59,Default,Smith,0,0,0,,{Duly received.}Đã xác nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.72,Default,Smith,0,0,0,,{I do apologize for the imposition.}Tôi rất xin lỗi vì sự bất tiện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.03,Default,Smith,0,0,0,,{Have a lovely trip, now.}Vậy thì xin hãy tận hưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:20.72,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Thanks a lot.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.10,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Hey, it's the little bird!}Đây là bé chim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.72,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{My outside persona, Mk II.}Bản thể thứ 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:34.03,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hello?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:36.57,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{No, not a problem.}Không có vấn đề gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.32,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yes, it's finished.}Vâng, đã hoàn thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:40.99,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.73,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yes, it has been received.}Vâng, vừa nhận được.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.75,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{No, thank you very much.}Không, cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.76,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yes. Thank you.}Vâng, cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.14,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Goodbye, then.}Vậy thì tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:54.59,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Was that Gene?}Gene à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:58.17,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{He's not "Gene." \NHe's Vice-Director Junghardt.}Không phải Gene. Phó giám đốc Junghardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.01,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Keep business and private matters separate.}Công tư phân minh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:01.89,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{So...}Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.69,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What did he say?}Ông ấy nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:04.82,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{About what?}Nói gì là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.90,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Well, I mean... Work's been \Ngoing really well, so...}À thì... công việc suôn sẻ nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:13.02,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I was just wondering what \Nhe thought about that...}Nên tôi tự hỏi ông ấy thấy sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.64,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I guess.}Vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.24,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Your big brother said he has high hopes.}Anh trai yêu dấu nói là kì vọng lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:21.39,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Really?!}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.02,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Yeah. For me.}Ừm, kì vọng ở tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:26.00,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{He said to keep taking good care of you.}Rằng hãy chăm sóc cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.56,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.90,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,Nius...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.49,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,Achillus... Viola...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.58,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{The Immortal Nine... The nine who never die.}Chín kẻ bất tử... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.15,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{No...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.96,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{I guess it's really six now.}Có vẻ chỉ còn lại 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.59,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{Vice-Director Junghardt.}Phó giám đốc Junghardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.51,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{We've received a report that the id \Nretrieved from Viola has left Mars.}Chúng tôi vừa nhận báo cáo ID \Nthu hồi từ Viola đã rời khỏi Sao Hoả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.84,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{But Ochrona seems to be \Nnosing around, as well.}Nhưng Ochrona cũng đang rình mò gần đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.15,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{We certainly wouldn't want \Nthem finding out about it.}Để chúng phát hiện ra đúng là phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.77,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{Measures will be taken.}Vậy tôi sẽ tiến hành xử lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.88,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{Also, regarding the traveling carnival...}Ngoài ra, về lễ hội...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.73,DefaultItalics,Gregory,0,0,0,,{The town where Rouge currently is...}Thành phố nơi Rouge đang ở...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.51,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{They're putting on a show \Nin Wellstown, right?}Một buổi biểu diễn ở Wellstown à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.64,Default,Gene,0,0,0,,{And that doesn't seem to be mere coincidence.}Có vẻ không chỉ là trùng hợp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:57.44,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{It seems we'll find a lead on our next target,\NPhantom Verde, in the Nean settlement.}Có vẻ chúng ta sẽ tìm thấy manh mối của mục tiêu \Ntiếp theo, Phantom Verde, ở khu định cư Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:01.12,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Don't the Immortal Nine take human forms?}Tưởng bọn chúng lấy nhân dạng con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.39,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{They might be hiding among the Neans, \Ndisguised as Neans.}Có thể chúng ẩn náu trong các Neans, \Ncải trang thành một Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.76,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{That's Investigator Ash from Ochrona.}Điều tra viên Ash từ Ochrona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.52,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{He sure went to a lot of trouble, \Ncoming all the way to Mars.}Đến tận đây làm việc đúng là vất vả.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.02,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{He's from Ochrona?}Ông ta từ Ochrona à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.85,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hm? Oh, I saw him on the list.}Hm... Tôi có thấy trên danh sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:22.56,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Something about an old man \Non the rebound, or something.}Hình như là đang hồi phục hay gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:26.27,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,Neans, Neans, Neans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.28,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What the hell is going on?}Cái quái gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.52,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{Of course they're here.}Dĩ nhiên phải ở đây rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:33.03,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{The biggest Nean settlement \Non Mars is in this city.}Khu định cư Neans lớn nhất nằm ở đây mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.31,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Bet you're thrilled to have so many \Nof your own kind around, huh?}Cậu vui vì có nhiều đồng loại nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:44.04,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You have to go through a heavily \Nguarded gate to enter the settlement.}Phải đi qua một cổng bảo vệ \Nnghiêm ngặt mới được vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:48.21,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Only registered Neans and authorized \Npersonnel can pass through.}Chỉ những Neans đã đăng kí và\N người uỷ quyền mới được vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.97,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{What did Gene say?}Gene nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.54,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Dumped it all on us.}Chúng ta tự xử.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.89,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Seriously. Don't come up with \Nonly half a date plan, damn it.}Thiệt tình, đã nghĩ ra kế hoạch \Nhẹn hò thì nghĩ đến hết đi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.36,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Whole boiled herm is so good!}Luộc nguyên con ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:12.19,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh? It's gone... It's gone!}Ủa? Đâu mất rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.24,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.12,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{My chocolate is gone.}Socola mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.14,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I know I still had more!}Đáng ra phải còn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.58,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Your chocolate? Oh, I know where that is.}Socola? A, tôi biết nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:23.97,Flashback,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Here you go.}Của em đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.26,Flashback,Miguel/Emily,0,0,0,,{Thank you!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.09,Flashback,Emily,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye!}Tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.54,Flashback,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Be sure to brush your teeth.}Nhớ đánh răng sau khi ăn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.88,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You grew up a little by giving \Nthose kids chocolate, right?}Cô đã trưởng thành vì cho chúng nó socola mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.49,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Good for you.}Tuyệt vời lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.93,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I'm going to buy more.}Tôi sẽ đi mua thêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.09,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{No, you're not.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.15,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{We're having a strategy meeting.}Chúng ta phải họp bàn kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:42.10,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Jill said I was free!}Jill nói tôi được tự do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:46.10,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Jill? Why bring up that camera nerd now?}Jill? Tại sao lại lôi tên cô ta ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.27,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{She said freedom means \NI can make my own choices.}Cô ấy nói tôi được tự do chọn lựa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.11,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hah. Freedom? You know there's no such thing.}Tự do? Cô cũng hiểu là làm gì có chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.03,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{There is!}Có!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.08,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.28,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Acting on your own free will \Ndisqualifies you as an agent.}Tự ý hành động là thất bại của một điệp vụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.62,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I always fight of my own free will.}Tôi lúc nào cũng tự do chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.29,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{All you do is stand behind me and watch!}Cô chỉ biết đứng sau và xem thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:08.76,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Don't get smart with the person \Nwho makes all that possible for you.}Đừng có tự mãn với người đã làm mọi chuyện cho cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.71,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{You're nothing but a tool for Aletheia.}Cô chẳng khác gì công cụ của Aletheia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.00,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Just a piece of equipment, really.}Chỉ là một sản phẩm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.24,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Hey...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.03,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Welp, she's gone.}Đi mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.40,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Stupid Naomi! Stupid Naomi!}Naomi ngu ngốc! Naomi ngu ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.51,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Stupid Naomi! Stupid Naomi! Stupid Naomi!}{Stupid Naomi! Stupid Naomi!}Naomi ngu ngốc! Naomi ngu ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.04,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid.}Ngốc, ngốc, ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.04,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid.}Ngốc, ngốc, ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.60,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid.}Ngốc, ngốc, ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.90,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Hey! You just touched me!}Này, vừa chạm vào tao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.13,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{I didn't.}Không có.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.71,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{You just did! See?}Đấy! Chạm vào nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:59.89,Default,Troop2,0,0,0,,{Whew, scary. Imagine a Nean \Ntouching a human without permission.}Sợ quá. Một Nean dám chạm vào\N con người khi chưa được phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.25,Default,Troop2,0,0,0,,{It must be broken.}Hình như nó hỏng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.01,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Yeah, definitely broken.}Phải rồi, hỏng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.40,Default,Troop2,0,0,0,,{And broken tools must be disposed of.}Bị hỏng thì phải xử lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.60,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Please wait a minute. I haven't...}Khoan đã. Tôi có làm gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.27,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Shut up, Scar Head!}Im mồm, đầu sẹo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.78,Default,Troop2,0,0,0,,{Let's take you to where you'll be dealt with.}Dẫn nó đến khu vực xử lý nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.77,Default,Troop3,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Mày là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.11,Default,Troop3,0,0,0,,{What're you lookin' at? Hey!}Nhìn cái gì? Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.49,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Bitch!}Con chó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.16,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,Nằm sấp xuống!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.33,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Neans are not tools.}Neans không phải công cụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.08,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Or equipment!}Cũng như sản phẩm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.50,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{What are you?}Mày muốn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.00,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Rion, what's all this?}Rion, sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.13,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Doctor Afdal!}Bác sĩ Afdal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.89,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Doctor Afdal. You know this boy?}Người quen của bác sĩ ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.64,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{He's my assistant.}Là trợ lý của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.44,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{Ah, I see.}A, hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:43.26,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{That girl over there, too?}Còn con nhỏ kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.45,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that's right.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.24,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{All right, then. Yo, let's go.}Được rồi, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.88,Default,Troop2,0,0,0,,{What? But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.65,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{The doctor's always been good to us.}Bác sĩ lúc nào cũng giúp đỡ chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.29,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{I'm counting on you to bring us \Nthe you-know-what again.}Tôi mong lại được sử dụng thứ đó lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.22,Default,Troop1,0,0,0,,{C'mon, let's go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.45,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Rion, don't make trouble.}Rion, đừng gây rắc rối chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.82,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,Tôi rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.83,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Let's go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.71,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.46,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Oh!}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.72,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Uh, I mean...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.34,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{O-Over there!}B-Bên kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.01,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{You want in there?}Cô muốn vào à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.97,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Someone I'm looking for is in there.}Tôi đang tìm người trong đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.68,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Yeah, of course.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:30.90,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Come.}Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.73,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Doctor?}Bác sĩ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.83,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,Các anh vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.77,Default,Troop4,0,0,0,,{Hm? Ah.}Hm? A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.65,Default,Troop4,0,0,0,,{Doctor Afdal.}Bác sĩ Afdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.54,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{I'm against this.}Tôi phản đối điều này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:01.22,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{She may be an Alter. It's too dangerous.}Cô ấy có thể là Alter nhưng vẫn rất nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.04,Default,Huey,0,0,0,,{No, she isn't...}Không, cô ấy không...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.30,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Shut up, Nean outsider.}Người ngoài thì im lặng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.84,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Humans are looking for \Nan excuse to destroy us.}Con người đang tìm cớ để tiêu diệt chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.22,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{There's no need for us to meet \Nwith an unknown Nean.}Không cần phải gặp một Nean không xác định.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.42,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{No, let's meet with her.}Không, hãy gặp cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.31,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,Juval!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:19.03,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{What we need is hope.}Chúng ta cần hi vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:22.57,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Even if it's only as much as \Nthe thinnest spider's thread.}Dù hi vọng đó có nhỏ nhoi như sợi tơ nhện đi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.09,Default,Nean2,0,0,0,,{Doctor!}Bác sĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.17,Default,Nean3,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness!}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.91,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Did something happen?}Có chuyện gì xảy ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.46,Default,Nean4,0,0,0,,{Doctor, we need help! It's Dahlia!}Bác sĩ, là Dahlia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.58,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Hold her down!}Giữ chặt cô ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.22,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.80,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{You! Come help!}Cả cô nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.27,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Quit dawdling!}Còn đứng đó làm gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:02.58,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{All good now.}Ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.34,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.40,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,Dahlia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:10.53,Default,Dahlia,0,0,0,,{Doctor... Thank you.}Bác sĩ... cảm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.77,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Dahlia is stable now.}Dahlia đã ổn định lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.61,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{It's a temporary fix.}Chỉ tạm thời thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.88,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{She won't get better?}Cô ấy không khoẻ hơn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.05,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Her signals are out of sync.}Tín hiệu không đồng bộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.51,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{But if I let her die, \Nher employer will give me hell.}Nhưng nếu để cô ta chết,\Nchủ nhân của Dahlia sẽ giết tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.35,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Why would they do that?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:36.23,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{People who hire combat \NNeans receive a subsidy.}Những người thuê Neans \Nchiến đấu sẽ nhận được trợ cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.65,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{It means they don't even \Nhave the freedom to die.}Tức là họ không có quyền được chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.05,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{That's cruel.}Thật tàn nhẫn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.11,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{They're still better off here than elsewhere.}Nơi đây còn tốt hơn nhiều chỗ khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:47.74,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{The Neans they're throwing \Nat the Venus Project}Những Neans tham gia dự án Venus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:51.04,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{are being worked to death in \Nthat planet's harsh environment.}đang phải làm việc đến chết trên hành tinh này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:56.07,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{They work only for the \Nterraforming of a world}Họ làm việc cải tạo thế giới
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.77,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{so hellish that humans can't \Ntouch or even look at it,}ở những nơi kinh khủng mà con\N người không thể đến được.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.59,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{and then they die.}Và họ chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.35,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{They're literally consumable goods.}Đúng nghĩa một sản phẩm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.97,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Anyway, where are you headed?}Thế cô định đi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.88,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{You said there's someone \Nhere you're looking for?}Cô nói tìm ai đó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:16.52,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Huh? Oh, uh...}Hả? À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.04,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Where should I go, I wonder?}Tôi phải đi đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:19.89,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:24.86,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{He's very cunning. I don't know where he is.}Hắn ta rất xảo quyệt nên tôi chẳng biết hắn ở đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.22,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{You're pretty funny.}Cô thú vị nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.49,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{You are Rouge, yes?}Cô là Rouge nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:36.87,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{I am Levi 328 of the CFN.}Tôi là Levi 328 của CFN.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.50,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{CF...?}CF?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.75,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{The Council of Free Neans.}Hội đồng những Neans tự do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.58,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{I represent someone who \Nwishes to meet with you.}Tôi đại diện cho người muốn gặp cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.52,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{What now? At this rate...}Giờ sao? Cứ thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:57.50,Default,Giallon,0,0,0,,{Looks like things aren't going your way.}Có vẻ mọi chuyện không suôn sẻ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.05,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Chief!}Giám đốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.47,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{About that investigation \Ndata I asked you for...}Về việc dữ liệu điều tra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.21,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{Eh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.36,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{The case of the red silhouette!}Vụ án tên đồ đỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.94,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{That one that recently showed up \Nagain in Canal City!}Kẻ xuất hiện ở thành phố Canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.34,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I'm busy right now.}Xin lỗi, ta đang rất bận.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.15,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Wai—}Khoa--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.11,Default,Police,0,0,0,,{I'm very sorry. I must ask you to leave.}Tôi rất xin lỗi nhưng anh hãy đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.98,Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,{He's from Ochrona. You sure about this?}Tên đó từ Ochrona. Vậy ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.62,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{Just leave him.}Cứ kệ hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.79,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Damn it.}Mẹ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.15,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{Smoking is prohibited inside this building.}Hút thuốc bị cấm ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.79,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What about those guys, then?}Mấy tên kia thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.64,Default,Noid,0,0,0,,{I'll warn them.}Tôi sẽ cảnh báo họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.33,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Whoa, whoa, whoa! Don't!}Này này này! Đừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.52,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I went too far.}Mình nói quá rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:44.14,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{A tool for Aletheia? Equipment?}Công cụ của Aletheia? Sản phẩm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.50,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I guess I'm still pretty immature, too.}Có vẻ mình vẫn còn trẻ con quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:56.07,Flashback,Naomi,0,0,0,,{It seems we'll find a lead on our next target,\NPhantom Verde, in the Nean settlement.}Có vẻ chúng ta sẽ tìm thấy mục\N tiêu ở khu định cư Neans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.17,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Did she go alone?}Không lẽ đi một mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.32,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Nah, no way.}Không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.32,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{No way... No way?}Làm gì có... nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.24,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Huey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.54,Default,Huey,0,0,0,,{I'm certain of it.}Không thể nhầm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.23,Default,Huey,0,0,0,,{This is the girl I saw \Nturning into the red figure.}Là cô gái tôi thấy biến thành màu đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.97,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.96,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Pleasure to meet you, Rouge. I'm Juval.}Rất vui được gặp cô, Rouge. Tôi là Juval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.44,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:25.15,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{What would the CFN want with a human?}CFN muốn gì ở một con người?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.47,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Who knows?}Ai biết chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.97,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{But you keep yourself clear \Nof dangerous guys like that.}Nhưng đừng dính dáng đến những kẻ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.60,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{How can they be dangerous?}Họ nguy hiểm lắm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.85,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{We aren't even capable of violence.}Chúng tôi đâu thể bạo lực được?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:41.32,Default,Dahlia,0,0,0,,{The CFN is only trying to win the right \Nfor Neans to live in freedom.}CFN chỉ đang cố giành quyền tự do cho Neans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.26,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{That's how it starts out, \Nno matter who's doing it.}Mọi chuyện lúc đầu thì như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:47.71,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{"We only want to live. \NWe only want to be free."}"Chúng tôi chỉ muốn sống, chúng tôi muốn tự do"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.34,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Eventually, that's not enough anymore.}Nhưng điều đó sẽ trở nên không đủ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.50,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{Neans are every bit as greedy as humans.}Neans sẽ trở nên tham lam như con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.13,Default,Dahlia,0,0,0,,{But if nothing else,}Nhưng ít nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:59.18,Default,Dahlia,0,0,0,,{humans aren't sent to war \Nthe moment they're born.}con người không phải ra chiến\N trường khi họ mới sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:04.97,Default,Dahlia,0,0,0,,{I've only ever known the battlefield, \Nthis town, and the factory.}Tôi chỉ biết đến chiến trường,\N thành phố này và nhà máy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.51,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,Dumas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.89,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Doctor Afdal.}Bác sĩ Afdal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.84,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{It's been a long time.}Đã lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.44,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{After the signing of the ceasefire \Nagreement with the Usurpers,}Sau khi kí thoả thuận ngừng bắn với Kẻ chiếm đoạt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:22.53,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{this town was built for the Neans \Nreturning from the war.}thành phố này được xây dựng\N cho Neans trở về sau trận chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:27.03,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{At first, we were permitted \Nto govern ourselves.}Lúc đầu, chúng tôi được tự quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.45,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{But now...}Nhưng hiện tại...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.96,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{The movement for autonomy is at a standstill,}Phong trào đòi quyền tự trị đang bị đình trệ,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.34,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{thanks to the wedge driven \Ndeeply into our consciousness:}nhờ thứ đã tiêm sâu vào tiềm thức của chúng ta:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.27,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{the Asimov Code.}Mã Asimov.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.32,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{We cannot harm humans.}Chúng ta không thể làm hại con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.56,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{We must obey the orders of humans.}Phải tuân lệnh của họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.81,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{We must protect our own existence.}Và phải bảo vệ họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:17.45,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{My third set of parents \Nwas an old human couple.}Cha mẹ thứ 3 của tôi là một cặp vợ chồng già.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.08,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{They were very kind.}Họ rất tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:24.20,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{I was made as a substitute child \Nfor humans who couldn't bear their own.}Tôi được tạo ra dành cho những cặp đôi hiếm muộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.57,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{I have had 23 human parents.}Tôi có 23 cha mẹ con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.87,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{There were some who used Juval, \Na permanent child, for evil.}Vài người lợi dụng Juval cho mục đích xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.11,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{What did I just say? Some were kind, too.}Tôi đã nói rồi mà, cũng có vài người tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:41.81,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{All we want is to live in freedom.}Bọn tôi chỉ là muốn được tự do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.82,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Freedom...}Tự do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:46.82,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{The Alters...}Những Alter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.28,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{are a group of Neans who try to \Nrebel against humans by force.}là một nhóm Neans nổi loạn chống lại con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.16,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{There are some like that, yes.}Đúng là có điều đó thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.05,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{We even have contact with them.}Chúng tôi đã tiếp xúc với họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.29,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Even with the Asimov Code in place?}Ngay cả khi có mã Asimov?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.21,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{I don't really know all the details.}Tôi không rõ chi tiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.45,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{They might be the people I'm chasing after.}Có thể chúng là những kẻ tôi đang tìm kiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.47,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{You said you can contact them?}Cậu nói có thể liên lạc với chúng?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.09,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{They seem to have an informant \Nwithin this settlement.}Có vẻ chúng có kẻ cung cấp\N thông tin trong khu định cư này.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.72,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Do you know who it is?}Cậu biết là ai không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.02,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{You do?}Không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.08,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Not for certain.}Tôi không chắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.53,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{But whoever it is...}Nhưng nếu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:26.27,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{What we seek is not your strength.}Thứ tôi tìm kiếm không phải sức mạnh của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.11,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{It's your free will.}Mà là ý chí tự do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.67,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{You aren't bound by the Asimov Code.}Cô không bị ràng buộc bởi mã Asimov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.14,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{You interact with humans as an equal.}Cô tương tác với con người bình đẳng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:37.02,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{That gives your existence \Nitself great meaning.}Sự tồn tại của cô mang ý nghĩa to lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:43.69,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Even just knowing that a Nean like you \Nexists and walks in step with us}Chỉ cần một Nean như cô bước đi cạnh chúng tôi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:46.42,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{will give many Neans hope.}cũng đủ để mang lại hi vọng cho Neans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.84,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Give Neans... hope?}Mang lại hi vọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:53.46,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Of course, you don't need \Nto answer right away.}Dĩ nhiên cô không cần trả lời ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:57.73,Default,Juval,0,0,0,,{Take your time thinking about it \Nduring your stay here.}Cứ từ từ suy nghĩ trong khi còn ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:05.94,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Well, then, Doctor Afdal, \NI'll be counting on you.}Vậy thì bác sĩ Afdal, nhờ anh cả đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.17,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{He's as full of shit as ever.}Vẫn khốn nạn như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.41,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Doctor!}Bác sĩ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.81,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{It's... It's Dahlia!}Là Dahlia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.38,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{I'm sure she's grateful to you.}Cô ấy hẳn sẽ rất biết ơn bác sĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.95,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{The battlefield, this town, and the factory...}Chiến trường, thành phố này và nhà máy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.60,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{She said those were all she ever knew.}Là những nơi cô ấy biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.83,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{This city is all I know.}Tôi chỉ biết mỗi thành phố này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:39.67,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{I've lived here, helping you, \Never since I was born.}Tôi sống ở đây, phụ giúp bác sĩ từ khi sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.37,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{If I can learn techniques from you \Nthat I can use to help my kind...}Nếu có thể học được từ bác sĩ, \Ntôi có thể giúp những Neans khác...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.75,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{What did I tell you? \NThat's always how it starts.}Tôi đã nói rồi, ban đầu thì ai cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.04,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{But soon...}Nhưng sớm thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.57,Default,Afdal,0,0,0,,{that won't be enough.}mọi chuyện sẽ trở nên không đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.72,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Doctor?}Bác sĩ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.16,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Tools.}Công cụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.79,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Equipment.}Sản phẩm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.46,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Freedom.}Tự do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.53,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Hope...}Hi vọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:13.02,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I wonder what Naomi would say.}Naomi thì sẽ nói gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.74,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.60,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{Juval wishes to see you.}Juval muốn gặp cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.27,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.03,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{She got into the settlement on her own!}Tự xâm nhập vào luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.84,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{She's more competent than I thought!}Giỏi hơn mình nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:36.36,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,{He said to have you come in alone.}Cậu ấy nói cô có thể vào một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.46,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.35,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{What the heck are you doing?}Cô đang làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.72,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,{I didn't do it!}Tôi không có làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.84,DefaultItalics,Naomi,0,0,0,,{I know that. So who's the kid?}Biết rồi. Thế đứa trẻ nào kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.44,Default,Rouge,0,0,0,,Juval.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.60,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Juval?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.42,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Juval...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.97,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,Juval 087...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.40,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Dang, he's a big fish!}Vãi, hàng thật luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.72,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,Juval!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.66,Default,Nean5,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me you...}Không lẽ cô...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.24,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Everyone, calm down.}Tất cả bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.97,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{Let's keep this quiet for a while.}Hãy tạm thời đừng nói ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.79,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{But...!}Nhưng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:32.29,Default,Dumas,0,0,0,,{If the humans find out, \Nthey'll try to meddle in our affairs.}Nếu con người biết được, chúng sẽ can thiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.51,Default,Levi,0,0,0,,{Well...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.30,Default,Security Officer,0,0,0,,{Hm? Ah, Doctor. Is something the matter?}Bác sĩ? Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.06,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Chief!}Giám đốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.70,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What's all the fuss?}Có vụ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.04,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{I'm sending a security force \Nto the Nean settlement.}Ta gửi đội trị an đến khu định cư Neans
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:49.94,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{What happened?}Chuyện gì đã xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:53.27,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{Ochrona or not, this area \Nis under our jurisdiction.}Ochrona hay gì đi nữa thì đây cũng\N là nơi bọn ta quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.68,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{I'd prefer it if you stayed out of this.}Đừng có nhúng mũi vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.42,Default,Ash,0,0,0,,{Aren't we both public servants?}Chẳng phải chúng ta đều là công chức sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.80,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.16,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{Did she get set up by those Alter guys?}Bị đám Alter đó lừa à...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.08,Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Mình nên làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
